Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.26,0:04:10.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A father-son that are like peas in a pod.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.36,0:04:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be working then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.33,0:04:12.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The one sending off...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:15.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,understands how the one being sent-off feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.03,0:04:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha0\t(1659,0,\alphaFF)}Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.84,0:04:18.94,Studio,,0,0,0,,He's hesitating.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.20,0:04:21.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Alright. Off he goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.04,0:04:23.04,Studio,,0,0,0,,Oh. He's running.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.18,0:04:28.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The bus stop is across the road from the beauty parlor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.28,0:04:32.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His father tried to time it with the bus timetable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:36.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And Ritsuki should make it just in time however...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.32,0:04:38.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But looking at the timetable again...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.09,0:04:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha0\t(3090,0,\alphaFF)}The first bus to arrive will not be the right one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.79,0:04:41.46,Studio,,0,0,0,,{\alpha0\t(3090,0,\alphaFF)}Oh no.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.53,0:04:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,A bus that won't reach home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:46.23,Studio,,0,0,0,,- Oh no.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.06,0:04:46.23,Studio,,0,0,0,,- No good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.26,0:04:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(285,531)\fs40}Zanezawa eigyoujyo
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.26,0:04:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(285,409)\fs40}Kitanakayama Nishinakayama
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.26,0:04:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(285,281)\fs40}Kitanakayama
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.23,0:04:49.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next one is going to Zanezawa
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.40,0:04:54.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,but to get home he needs to ride the bus to Nishinakayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.34,0:04:56.44,Studio,,0,0,0,,- That's bad. \N - He's definitely gonna board it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.11,0:04:59.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't board the next bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.28,0:05:02.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Of course he can't read the destination on the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.25,0:05:07.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Would be good if he asked the driver. But he's not good at letting out his voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.25,0:05:07.25,Studio,,0,0,0,,- Looks bad. \N- What will he do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.25,0:05:08.89,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.89,0:05:11.06,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Are you heading to Nishinakayama?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.26,0:05:12.09,Studio,,0,0,0,,Ah, good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.36,0:05:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Nishinakayama?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.29,0:05:13.09,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.09,0:05:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry but I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.09,0:05:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, Ritsuki was able to ask loud and clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.33,0:05:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha0\t(2058,0,\alphaFF)}He didn't board it indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.64,0:05:25.50,Studio,,0,0,0,,What a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.40,0:05:30.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Truth is that he's been playing "bus pretend" in the bath with his brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.78,0:05:32.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His brother takes the role of the driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.84,0:05:35.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And Ritsuki is the passenger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.15,0:05:38.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And he will say: "Going to Nishiyama?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.15,0:05:39.98,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.98,0:05:43.86,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\alpha0\t(3596,0,\alphaFF)}Are you going to Nishiyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.69,0:05:48.09,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. Nishiy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.39,0:05:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.09,0:05:52.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The bus driver went as far as getting off the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.30,0:05:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha0\t(1920,0,\alphaFF)}I am going to Nishiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.63,0:05:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Please touch this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.30,0:05:58.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's going as far to teach him how to ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:05:59.70,Studio,,0,0,0,,How kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.74,0:06:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Touch here and then sit...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:05.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's even showing him a place to sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.31,0:06:05.98,Studio,,0,0,0,,How kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He boarded it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.62,0:06:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1215,999)}{\alphaFF\t(0,283,\alpha0)\t(4888,0,\alphaFF)\fs45}Filmed in 2016
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.48,0:06:13.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Just like the bus driver requested.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.65,0:06:16.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's holding on tight to the handrail.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:22.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:22.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.66,0:06:24.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He isn't scampering around today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.96,0:06:29.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Today he isn't even wearing his shoes on the wrong foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.23,0:06:29.83,Studio,,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.40,0:06:32.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Needs to go 10 bus stops.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.97,0:06:36.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But since it's the last stop he doesn't need to hit the stop button.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.78,0:06:39.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's riding while quietly listening to the driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.26,0:06:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for riding.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.89,0:06:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(3393,0,\alphaFF)}Last stop. Nishinakayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.80,0:07:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(1252,0,\alphaFF)}This is the last stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.33,0:07:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Please touch here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:03.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's even teaching him how to disembark.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.70,0:07:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(2460,0,\alphaFF)}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.51,0:07:13.01,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\t(3222,0,\alphaFF)}THANK YOU VERY MUCH.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.98,0:07:13.71,Studio,,0,0,0,,How remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.01,0:07:15.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's letting out his voice today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.92,0:07:23.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,"After the bus ride I'm counting on you."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.19,0:07:25.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's what his dad said over the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.79,0:07:29.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Will he be like: "I want to go back with mom?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.66,0:07:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.86,0:07:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Ricchi what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.10,0:07:33.87,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.37,0:07:36.40,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.50,0:07:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're busy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.90,0:07:38.17,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,The jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.17,0:07:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Jacket? {\alphaFF\t(921,921,\alpha0)} What's up with the jacket?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.37,0:07:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There it was. Daddy totally forgot it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.21,0:07:47.41,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.41,0:07:51.45,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,He's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.91,0:07:52.05,Studio,,0,0,0,,He's no good... hahaha
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.01,0:07:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,See Ricchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.62,0:07:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.59,0:07:55.12,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:56.62,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\t({(1222,0,\alphaFF))}It's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.62,0:08:00.73,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His mom, {\alphaFF\t(1157,1157,\alpha0)}is making sure to encourage Ritsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.73,0:08:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(2986,0,\alphaFF)}If it's too big then you should wear your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.90,0:08:05.33,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,No, it's small.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:07.63,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,It's huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.83,0:08:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You can lift your spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.87,0:08:12.74,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Aaaaaah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.90,0:08:14.17,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\t(826,0,\alphaFF)}Aaa-aaand
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.17,0:08:15.71,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\t(1024,0,\alphaFF)}Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.71,0:08:16.81,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\t(819,0,\alphaFF)}Aa-and
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.81,0:08:17.94,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\t(820,0,\alphaFF)}go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.94,0:08:20.41,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Cheer-ing squad
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.41,0:08:24.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With the jacket his grandmother made {\alphaFF\t(2292,2292,\alpha0)}he has powered up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.18,0:08:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(1858,0,\alphaFF)}I clawed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.09,0:08:37.06,RedFill,,0,0,0,,{\pos(603,517)}{\alphaFF\t(0,450,\alpha0)}Home
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.09,0:08:37.06,PurpleFill,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1200.643,199.864)}{\alphaFF\t(0,450,\alpha0)}Beauty parlor
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.09,0:08:37.06,OrangeFill,,0,0,0,,{\pos(999.857,62.424)}{\alphaFF\t(0,450,\alpha0)}Choumeigaoka sanchoume nishi
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.22,0:08:33.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The way back also has five bus routes, so he must ask if the bus will stop near the salon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.19,0:08:37.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Will he be able to say: Choumeigaokasanchoumenishi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.53,0:08:38.20,Studio,,0,0,0,,That's difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.49,0:08:38.20,Studio,,0,0,0,,Hey hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.23,0:08:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,One more time, what bus was it again? \N {\alphaFF\t(1588,1588,\alpha0)}Choumeigaokasanchoumenishi
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.56,0:08:41.37,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(723.429,927.78)}...choumenishi
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:45.14,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Choumeigaoka{\alphaFF\t(1785,1785,\alpha0)}sanchoumenishi
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.60,0:08:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.27,0:08:47.04,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Off you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:50.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It will be difficult from this point on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.64,0:08:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.61,0:08:56.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But in this outfit he will definitely give it his all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.31,0:08:58.85,Studio,,0,0,0,,- How cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.15,0:08:58.85,Studio,,0,0,0,,- Amazing. Looks like he's going into battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:09:01.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,At the crossing there are flags left there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.89,0:09:03.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ah, he has his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.69,0:09:05.16,Studio,,0,0,0,,He will use his own?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.82,0:09:06.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The flag of the cheering squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.02,0:09:08.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His mother made it by hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.13,0:09:09.89,Studio,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.76,0:09:13.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The scampering Ritsuki {\alphaFF\t(1689,1689,\alpha0)}is appearing to us like an entirely different person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.30,0:09:15.07,Studio,,0,0,0,,For real.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.14,0:09:18.87,Studio,,0,0,0,,Can he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.67,0:09:19.34,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\t(1388,0,\alphaFF)}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.91,0:09:22.14,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.14,0:09:27.11,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Are you going to Choumeigaoka sanchoume nishi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.11,0:09:28.95,Studio,,0,0,0,,He said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.61,0:09:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We go that way.{\alphaFF\t(1725,1725,\alpha0)} Please board.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.72,0:09:32.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He said it properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.82,0:09:35.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And what he learned before?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.39,0:09:36.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,To present the card.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.82,0:09:40.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This time he was asked to ride behind the driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.39,0:09:44.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Look look. He's properly holding on to the handrail.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.94,0:09:58.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Both his parents said: "Do your best."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.11,0:10:02.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And therefor Ritsuku has become more reliable than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.88,0:10:06.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's not the last stop so you better press the button.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.19,0:10:10.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The big birthday cake sign is the landmark visible from the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.29,0:10:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Next is Choumeigaoka Sanchoume West. {changed North to West, 西=West}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.49,0:10:16.23,Studio,,0,0,0,,It's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.16,0:10:15.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There. It's even being announced.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.23,0:10:17.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There. You better press it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.63,0:10:20.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Did he become sleepy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.40,0:10:21.26,Studio,,0,0,0,,Become sleepy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.26,0:10:24.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,An old lady is getting off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.77,0:10:25.77,Studio,,0,0,0,,How great.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.80,0:10:29.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The bus stopped at Choumeigaoka Sanchoume West. {changed North to West}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.38,0:10:34.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Oh no. You should get off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.41,0:10:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you not getting off?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.52,0:10:38.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.52,0:10:39.85,Studio,,0,0,0,,What a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.88,0:10:40.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Better listen to the driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.25,0:10:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We are at Choumeigaoka Sanchoume West. {changed North to West}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.55,0:10:44.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.74,0:10:45.52,Studio,,0,0,0,,How great.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.79,0:10:47.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was taught to get off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.19,0:10:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.53,0:10:53.26,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.16,0:10:54.00,Studio,,0,0,0,,How great.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.17,0:10:58.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Dad has been starring at the bus stop the entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.67,0:10:59.10,Studio,,0,0,0,,He's worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.57,0:11:01.84,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\t(1990,0,\alphaFF)}Daddy. Yahoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.41,0:11:05.88,Studio,,0,0,0,,He's so tiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.51,0:11:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.31,0:11:11.22,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Daddy, it was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.22,0:11:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.22,0:11:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.39,0:11:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You did well while going by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.59,0:11:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.66,0:11:20.43,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.43,0:11:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.23,0:11:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But you were able to go by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:29.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Now dad can be part of the Blue Skies Cheering Squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.63,0:11:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ritsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.17,0:11:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.44,0:11:35.97,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\t(2255,0,\alphaFF)}Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.87,0:11:41.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And now they are about to cheer his brother on for his birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.22,0:11:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(3421,0,\alphaFF)}Let's make it the best birthday for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.25,0:11:54.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With squad leader Taira in front Blue Skies have gathered.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.39,0:12:00.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Seeing the Blue Skies Cheering Squad up close.
