Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.16,0:14:48.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But he has a sweet spot for his eldest son, Iori.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.90,0:14:51.47,BlueFill,,0,0,0,,{\pos(477,513)}{\alphaFF\t(0,452,\alpha0)\fs40}Iori \N3 years\N6 months old
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.23,0:14:51.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And Iori knows that quite well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.47,0:14:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Iori come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.34,0:14:57.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is Iori and his first errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.14,0:14:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Iori. Ask grandpa
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.94,0:15:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,for crabs. {\alphaFF\t(2226,2226,\alpha0)}Get the best one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.78,0:15:05.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's right. Crabs are counted with the modifier "pai".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.72,0:15:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(2086,0,\alphaFF)}'K? Can you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.39,0:15:10.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He can't?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.06,0:15:17.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,400 meters down the same street to get grandpas to take him to the crab fish tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.96,0:15:19.63,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(847.5,947)}{\alphaFF\t(0,450,\alpha0)}Grandpa
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.96,0:15:19.63,RedFill,,0,0,0,,{\pos(325.5,297)}{\alphaFF\t(0,450,\alpha0)}Shop
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.96,0:15:19.63,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1029,109)}{\alphaFF\t(0,450,\alpha0)}Crab fish tank
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.13,0:15:19.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's what the entire errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.53,0:15:24.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,"I told you, I can't go daddy."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you go if I hug you once?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.90,0:15:30.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His dad is so soft on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.34,0:15:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you will go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.98,0:15:32.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His mothers eyes are shining.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.68,0:15:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.91,0:15:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you get lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.11,0:15:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.11,0:15:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1134,671.4)}{\alphaFF\t(0,326,\alpha0)}{\t(3329,0,\alphaFF)}Mother
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.15,0:15:41.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The mother is an Echizen woman. She's tough on her husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.82,0:15:43.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She grabbed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.99,0:15:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave him be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.32,0:15:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not going because you are putting it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.83,0:15:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You are so soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.19,0:15:51.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's beginning. The usual fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.96,0:15:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Fulfill your duty {\alphaFF\t(591,591,\alpha0)}seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.33,0:15:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave him alone if you want him to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.80,0:16:00.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hope they will forget all about the errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.20,0:16:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Please leave him be, dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.84,0:16:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(1689,0,\alphaFF)}You are not allowed to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.14,0:16:09.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Now that they went each their own way it means that daddy is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.05,0:16:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Iori. Go and come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.85,0:16:13.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His dad changed his way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.45,0:16:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no one who can go but you Iori.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.45,0:16:16.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.45,0:16:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Carry this. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.46,0:16:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Iori.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.52,0:16:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you not listen to your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.96,0:16:22.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's right. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.06,0:16:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.93,0:16:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Go and come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.36,0:16:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.30,0:16:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.13,0:16:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alphaFF\t(389,389,\alpha0)}{\t(1724,0,\alphaFF)}I want you to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.47,0:16:33.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Carrying him? Isn't that bad, dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.20,0:16:35.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Treating Iori like a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.67,0:16:38.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's taking him to where his mother can't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.18,0:16:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alphaFF\t(0,418,\alpha0)}Ok? I'm begging you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.48,0:16:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If you listen to your daddy
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.81,0:16:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(2827,0,\alphaFF)}I will take you to your favorite place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.62,0:16:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? Go and get the crabs. Listen to your daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.76,0:16:52.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,No good dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.66,0:16:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(2088,0,\alphaFF)}Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.46,0:16:58.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is a test of endurance for the father.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.26,0:17:02.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But hey Iori. Dad is different today from his usual self.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.23,0:17:04.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He will quit it eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.94,0:17:06.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He will come to get him back, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.81,0:17:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You are still lingering around?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.42,0:17:20.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Worried of a grinning mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.02,0:17:23.59,Studio,,0,0,0,,What is she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.99,0:17:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I will lend you the sword, Iori, since you are a scaredy cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.62,0:17:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(1726,0,\alphaFF)}You're not strong, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want the sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.93,0:17:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you take the sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:33.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's Iori's cherished sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.96,0:17:37.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He will likely grow strong as soon as she gives it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.24,0:17:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Take the sword. How cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.67,0:17:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you be a man, Iori?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.61,0:17:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you go? Won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.94,0:17:46.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I won't. I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.94,0:17:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(702.857,110.847)}TN: They are speaking in a heavy dialect and this time the narrator is mimicking him thus the faint studio laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.84,0:17:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be watching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.18,0:17:54.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,For his first errand his mother must battle it out with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.95,0:17:56.69,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.92,0:18:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Only babies want to be held and hold hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.12,0:18:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A baby after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:03.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His mother withdrew her hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.36,0:18:06.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,If she holds out her hands here he will want to be cuddled even further.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.63,0:18:08.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His mother knows that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.97,0:18:10.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The kind smell of his mothers apron.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.87,0:18:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be laughed at by babies like a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.60,0:18:14.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But today is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.31,0:18:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(2853,0,\alphaFF)}Then you can't be a big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.11,0:18:20.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's no good hitting her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.95,0:18:22.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Nor is hugging her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.88,0:18:25.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Or flailing and making a scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.92,0:18:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.02,0:18:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you back in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.56,0:18:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward and walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.46,0:18:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward and walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.93,0:18:39.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,While withdrawing her hands his mother thinks of a new strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.20,0:18:40.33,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If you walk over to that electric pole
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.87,0:18:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,then I will walk right behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.54,0:18:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward and walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.87,0:18:51.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She will make him walk a little more and more by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.05,0:18:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.28,0:18:59.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And without forgetting to praise him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.18,0:19:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You've walked this far?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.72,0:19:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's home? Iori's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.72,0:19:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You've walked so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.62,0:19:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Go the yellow circle next.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.99,0:19:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.40,0:19:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.27,0:19:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a bit more until the yellow circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.50,0:19:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:23.27,Studio,,0,0,0,,- He's not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.17,0:19:23.27,Studio,,0,0,0,,- Not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.87,0:19:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.04,0:19:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, just a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.11,0:19:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Your feet are outside of it. Go to the middle .
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.65,0:19:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.45,0:19:32.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She keeps her promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.92,0:19:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,See? I actually came.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.25,0:19:37.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hehe. He has started having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.22,0:19:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Next... next, go to where that line is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.19,0:19:48.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And like that Iori's mother increased the distance bit by bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.00,0:19:53.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,For his first errand his mother's strategy is necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.87,0:19:57.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His grandfather should be at the seashore at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.98,0:20:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Cross. Iori cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.58,0:20:03.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Alright. He went.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.15,0:20:05.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's alright now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.22,0:20:07.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Echizen women are strict with their boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.38,0:20:08.85,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.85,0:20:09.85,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.85,0:20:11.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But she's also kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.79,0:20:13.32,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.76,0:20:15.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's running.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.06,0:20:17.80,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\t(2456,0,\alphaFF)}Crab. Crab. Crab.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.90,0:20:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Iori. What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.33,0:20:21.83,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Crab.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.83,0:20:24.00,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I am here to get crabs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.00,0:20:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.34,0:20:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you told to collect crabs?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.74,0:20:28.67,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Yes, I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.67,0:20:29.91,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,But for grandpa
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:32.04,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,it might be a bit difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:34.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But you came to grandpa, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.25,0:20:36.98,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm getting the one in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.01,0:20:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You will?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.98,0:20:38.22,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Yeah, see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.22,0:20:39.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Like you were told by grandpa, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.88,0:20:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This one is huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.05,0:20:44.59,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,This one is huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.19,0:20:44.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He grabbed it with his hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.59,0:20:46.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Aren't you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.06,0:20:48.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,One crab is 20.000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.19,0:20:51.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was asked to only bring one crab.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.10,0:20:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can't carry it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine with just this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.80,0:20:58.07,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\t(1956,0,\alphaFF)}I don't just want that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.07,0:21:01.61,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I was told to get many crabs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.07,0:21:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\pos(685.714,60.509)}TN: The counter for (1) crab (ippai) makes it sound like many (ippai).
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.61,0:21:04.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,One (/Many)? That would mean one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.41,0:21:07.01,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,We better get more crabs.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.01,0:21:09.95,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Otherwise my mom won't be glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.95,0:21:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to make her happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.12,0:21:14.72,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,This one is small.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.22,0:21:18.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He intends to bring the biggest ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.22,0:21:21.03,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\t(2526,0,\alphaFF)}This one is huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.49,0:21:23.56,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,This one is the biggest one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.56,0:21:26.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,An even bigger crab than the previous one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.40,0:21:28.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's not afraid of the pincers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.67,0:21:31.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As expected from a child of the seashore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.77,0:21:37.01,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Heave-ho​. Heave-ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.87,0:21:37.01,Studio,,0,0,0,,I bet it's heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.01,0:21:39.54,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Big brother. {\alphaFF\t(1353,1353,\alpha0)}Big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.54,0:21:42.61,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I wonder if mom will be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.61,0:21:44.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's happy with himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.42,0:21:47.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Despite crying so much on the way there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.15,0:21:51.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Did he forget it all? Even the thing about the yellow circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.12,0:21:55.53,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,It's fine. I can go by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.53,0:21:57.43,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.96,0:22:01.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As long as Iori has his sword he's someone to be feared.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.10,0:22:03.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's fine. It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.80,0:22:07.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Even the customers are waiting for Iori's crabs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.61,0:22:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.24,0:22:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You came back?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.67,0:22:12.67,Studio,,0,0,0,,He came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.64,0:22:13.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It took him 5 minutes to walk back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.78,0:22:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.61,0:22:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You are such a well-behaved boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.55,0:22:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it to dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.65,0:22:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.79,0:22:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,said 1 crab so why {\alphaFF\t(1552,1552,\alpha0)}did you bring 2?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.66,0:22:28.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,One crab / many?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.66,0:22:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,About the crab
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.83,0:22:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,get 1 / many.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.76,0:22:35.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Didn't dad say to get many?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.10,0:22:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What a good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.17,0:22:41.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Don't gush all over me, mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.41,0:22:43.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I am a big brother after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.34,0:22:50.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They also sent a phone video from Iori's.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.35,0:22:52.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His father has it rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.68,0:22:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alphaFF\t(0,319,\alpha0)\fs40\pos(1234.972,933.112)}Filmed 2020 April 14th
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.18,0:22:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(86.4,405.8)}{\alphaFF\t(0,325,\alpha0)\t(4496,0,\alphaFF)}Dad
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.18,0:22:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1359.6,405.8)}{\alphaFF\t(0,325,\alpha0)\t(4496,0,\alphaFF)}Mom
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.22,0:22:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of the novel Corona
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.15,0:22:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,at our place
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.49,0:23:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,we've had about 300 cancellations from March to April.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.33,0:23:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I hesitated towards doing my best
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.80,0:23:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,despite the bleak outlook.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.27,0:23:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(3859,0,\alphaFF)}But now I've decided to put my all towards what I'm doing right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.61,0:23:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I just
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.68,0:23:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,don't want to lose {\alphaFF\t(2119,2119,\alpha0)}this fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.11,0:23:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to lose {\alphaFF\t(2259,2259,\alpha0)}to Corona. That's my intention. {typo: y -> my}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.89,0:23:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alphaFF\t(0,351,\alpha0)\pos(1277.829,998.712)}{\t(4221,0,\alphaFF)\fs40}At home in Tokyo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.59,0:23:32.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Iori is a company worker in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.02,0:23:34.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He is 27 and lives alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.89,0:23:37.66,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Even though you have a cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.63,0:23:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Haha, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.66,0:23:39.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,No no. He has a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.90,0:23:41.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's the one filming.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.83,0:23:44.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He washes his hands and gargles as a precaution against Corona.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.00,0:23:48.41,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\t(3126,0,\alphaFF)}I am working at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.54,0:23:52.01,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,And this type of work
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.01,0:23:56.95,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,is remote work on my computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.28,0:23:59.78,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,And even today I had meetings where...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.78,0:24:02.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,When he saw the accounting at his father's shop
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.55,0:24:07.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,he studied accounting at university and now works for a consulting firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.49,0:24:12.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's practiced, gotten 6 years of experience, and continued to improve.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.00,0:24:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1190.4,319.4)}{\alphaFF\t(0,319,\alpha0)}{\t(18804,0,\alphaFF)\fs45}Filmed by: Iori
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.60,0:24:18.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We only get to meet his girlfriend from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.74,0:24:24.31,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,My girlfriend is cleaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.54,0:24:24.31,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.31,0:24:27.28,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,A messy room {\alphaFF\t(1254,1254,\alpha0)}is a messy heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.78,0:24:28.48,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,1001)}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.28,0:24:29.71,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,You look at it constantly and think
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.48,0:24:29.71,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.71,0:24:33.08,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,{\t(3094,0,\alphaFF)}This is no good. {\alphaFF\t(925,925,\alpha0)}{\t(3094,0,\alphaFF)}The room is a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.38,0:24:36.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A perfect match for Iori.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.79,0:24:42.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The mother has decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.86,0:24:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096.8,868.2)}{\alphaFF\t(0,353,\alpha0)}{\t(4657,0,\alphaFF)}Mother
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.79,0:24:45.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,To create an errand on her day of giving birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.26,0:24:48.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,How surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.93,0:24:51.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,2 months before the expected date.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.90,0:24:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(749.142,915.976)}{\alphaFF\t(0,287,\alpha0)\fs50}{\t(4224,0,\alphaFF)}Ibaraki ● Jyousou city
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.90,0:24:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(677.142,92.542)}The city has a large expatriate population from Brazil, and many of the city signs are in both Japanese and Portuguese.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.94,0:24:55.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We met with them at the beginning of the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.44,0:24:57.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The mother had a single worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.14,0:25:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1209.6,991.4)}{\alphaFF\t(0,321,\alpha0)}{\t(3891,0,\alphaFF)\fs50}Filmed in 1996.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.41,0:25:00.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,About Hideki who is the middle child of 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.14,0:25:03.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Who is a kind and easy to comprehend boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.44,0:25:04.62,BlueFill,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1022.4,183.4)}{\alphaFF\t(0,325,\alpha0)}{\t(3896,0,\alphaFF)\fs45}Hideki\N4 years 10 months
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.08,0:25:05.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As the mother's stomach grows larger,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.42,0:25:08.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's worried he'll become jealous of the attention given to the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.29,0:25:11.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And that's why his mother decided
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.29,0:25:14.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,to put him on an errand on the day of the birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.46,0:25:16.06,BlueFill,,0,0,0,,{\pos(319.2,321)\fs40}Hideki\N4 years 10 months
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.46,0:25:16.06,PurpleFill,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1106.4,519.4)\fs40}Natsuki \N 1 year 11 months
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.12,0:25:16.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,An errand for the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.16,0:25:19.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Something that will change Hideki as a big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.26,0:25:23.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And suddenly the contractions began.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.40,0:25:28.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,"Hideki, your mother is giving it her all so let's all do our best."
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.67,0:25:33.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's what his father told him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.91,0:25:38.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And then it happened while the kids were at the pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.62,0:25:43.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Predicting this his mother made a phone guide.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.62,0:25:47.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\s1}If you{\s0} Use this to get to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.19,0:25:51.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And his father hurried to the hospital from his workplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.86,0:25:56.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's the dad. He can't know when the actual birth will take place.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.46,0:25:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1329.6,657)}{\alphaFF\t(0,325,\alpha0)}{\t(4029,0,\alphaFF)\fs45}Father
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.23,0:25:59.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's a crucial time.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.17,0:26:02.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And he asked the kids to jump on a taxi and ride to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.47,0:26:04.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And that's the errand that his mother thought up.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.21,0:26:08.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The kids should be back by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.92,0:26:14.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hideki and his little sister Natsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.15,0:26:16.35,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.35,0:26:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hideki. It's dad. {\alphaFF\t(1025,1025,\alpha0)}Mom still hasn't given birth...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.99,0:26:18.82,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,1001)}{\t(1533,0,\alphaFF)}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.86,0:26:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,but the baby will be born soon so
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.59,0:26:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,can you call a taxi and {\alphaFF\t(1358,1358,\alpha0)}ride it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.09,0:26:25.13,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,1003)}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.13,0:26:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Next to the TV
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.86,0:26:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,your mother's maternity health record book can be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.44,0:26:33.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She forgot her maternity health book.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.97,0:26:36.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She needs it while giving birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.04,0:26:37.14,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.14,0:26:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you bring it with Natsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.38,0:26:39.41,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.41,0:26:41.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Natsuki is still only 1 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.85,0:26:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know where to find the wallet?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.82,0:26:48.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His mother's wallet. They will need money.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.12,0:26:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in her bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.29,0:26:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And then there is a basket. {\alphaFF\t(1685,1685,\alpha0)}For carrying the baby in.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.22,0:26:51.76,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(711.429,1010.085)}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.99,0:26:54.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Natsuki only has to follow along.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.36,0:26:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(4088,0,\alphaFF)\pos(865.5,335)}Baby basket.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.96,0:27:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Then call the taxi. {\alphaFF\t(2257,2257,\alpha0)}I'm relying on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.57,0:27:03.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Father, son and mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.50,0:27:05.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is the beginning of their fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.94,0:27:09.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is Hideki's first time calling for a taxi.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.18,0:27:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for calling. This is Kantetsu Taxi.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.42,0:27:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.59,0:27:24.92,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Please send a taxi.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.92,0:27:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(2225,0,\alphaFF)}Alright. We will be there soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.39,0:27:30.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was able to call for a taxi.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.23,0:27:32.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hideki is doing it properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.16,0:27:35.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And closing off the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.83,0:27:37.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.37,0:27:38.47,Studio,,0,0,0,,{\pos(223.286,75)}- Wow. Remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.07,0:27:38.47,Studio,,0,0,0,,{\pos(211.286,136.78)}- Remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.40,0:27:42.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And he put shoes on his sister Natsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.41,0:27:45.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And locked the front door.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.88,0:27:52.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We've asked for permission to film from the taxi company
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.85,0:27:57.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and we've placed cameras in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.79,0:28:01.83,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\t(2756,0,\alphaFF)}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.16,0:28:04.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Natsuki is not good with strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.66,0:28:08.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Especially old guys. She won't talk with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.67,0:28:10.97,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.77,0:28:13.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The driver came from the city over.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.74,0:28:15.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's his first time coming to this residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.94,0:28:18.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We have not told him where to go. {Typo}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.21,0:28:21.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We only asked him to go where the kids tell him to.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.41,0:28:24.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't cry, Natsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.92,0:28:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(1652,0,\alphaFF)}Were are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.25,0:28:30.25,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,My mother is
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.25,0:28:33.09,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,giving birth therefore
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.09,0:28:34.39,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,both of us are going there.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.39,0:28:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Which hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.03,0:28:39.43,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,It's called Shoujisensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.43,0:28:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know where?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.56,0:28:43.10,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\t(2321,0,\alphaFF)}I will teach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.70,0:28:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(1121,0,\alphaFF)\pos(720,999)}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.10,0:28:46.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is the first time for him to go to this hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.70,0:28:54.18,WhiteLightBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1266,695)}{\alphaFF\t(0,323,\alpha0)}Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.70,0:28:54.18,RedFill,,0,0,0,,{\pos(277.5,217)}{\alphaFF\t(0,323,\alpha0)}Home
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.27,0:28:50.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hideki has gone to this hospital several times with his mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.74,0:28:53.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,How well does he remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.18,0:28:57.35,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,At the place called Kobayashi Store
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.35,0:28:59.25,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,there's a traffic light.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.25,0:29:01.79,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\t(2256,0,\alphaFF)}And go straight from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.35,0:29:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(2256,0,\alphaFF)\pos(720,1005)}Straight ahead?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.22,0:29:06.02,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Ah, I {\alphaFF\t(1088,1088,\alpha0)}forgot the basket.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.02,0:29:08.83,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,The basket for the newborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.83,0:29:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to bring the basket?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.29,0:29:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.60,0:29:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we need to go back and get it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.87,0:29:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. A baby has been born?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.20,0:29:17.27,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.27,0:29:19.17,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,It looks like she's about to be born.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.17,0:29:20.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's right. At the hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.44,0:29:23.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,the mother hasn't given birth yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.58,0:29:29.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The brother went to bring the basket.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.11,0:29:31.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Huh? She's not crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.18,0:29:33.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Natsuki who is timid towards strangers. s
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.55,0:29:37.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The basket that will be used when leaving the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.32,0:29:43.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,About 13 km to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.56,0:29:47.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,If everything goes well they will be there in 15 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.80,0:29:49.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Alright. Passed the Kobayashi store.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.90,0:29:53.14,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,We could also go this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.14,0:29:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Which way?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.14,0:29:55.97,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Straight ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.97,0:29:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Straight ahead?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.81,0:29:59.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Looks like the contractions are getting stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.28,0:30:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The child will be here soon so please {\alphaFF\t(1857,1857,\alpha0)}hang in there.s
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.09,0:30:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.95,0:30:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If I continue straight, will we hit it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.32,0:30:13.99,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.99,0:30:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(720,95)}TN: He meant to say "Un so" (Mhm, that's right), but his nervousness made it sound like "Uso" (I lied). That's why the narrator is asking him if he's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.29,0:30:18.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,You okay? Hideki.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.54,0:30:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I call them?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.40,0:30:29.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Just before the birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.17,0:30:30.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They are parting now.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.67,0:30:33.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The mother insisted on walking there by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.81,0:30:36.21,Studio,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.91,0:30:36.21,Studio,,0,0,0,,Remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.92,0:30:42.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The strong father can't be of any help today.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.79,0:30:52.96,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Turn this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.80,0:30:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Turning this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.96,0:30:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a narrow road.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.53,0:30:55.37,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.53,0:30:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But we have to go this way, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.30,0:31:01.17,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,If we go this way it will be even closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.17,0:31:02.77,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I know it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.77,0:31:05.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Really? They've driven for more than 20 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.74,0:31:07.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They should've been there by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.68,0:31:12.45,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I've seen a show on TV about going on errands by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.28,0:31:16.12,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,And after seeing this I wanted to do my best
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.12,0:31:17.85,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,and that's why I'm doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.99,0:31:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.02,0:31:20.32,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,We are getting closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.32,0:31:22.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Is that really the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.93,0:31:25.46,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,We decided that I first
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.46,0:31:28.47,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,must go purchase a bald.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.46,0:31:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs46\pos(718.285,55.933)}Rice ball coated with sweetened red beans, soybean flour or sesame​
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.47,0:31:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,A (rice) ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.27,0:31:30.57,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,A bald.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.57,0:31:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's a bald?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.74,0:31:33.00,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,A bald is
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.00,0:31:34.57,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,it's like a coated rice ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.57,0:31:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Who will eat the bald?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.17,0:31:38.04,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.87,0:31:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see. Your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.78,0:31:41.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His mother never asked for a rice ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.88,0:31:43.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The battle has started inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.88,0:31:47.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His father is nervously moving like the second hand while waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.16,0:31:53.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The baby is about to be born.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.92,0:31:56.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Despite there not being a moment to spare, Hideki...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.19,0:31:57.39,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,We decided that I first
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.39,0:32:00.40,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,must go purchase a bald.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.40,0:32:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,A (rice) ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.26,0:32:02.53,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,A bald.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.53,0:32:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's a bald?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.60,0:32:04.94,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,A bald is
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.94,0:32:06.50,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,it's like a coated rice ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.50,0:32:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Who will eat the bald?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.10,0:32:09.97,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.94,0:32:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see. Your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.61,0:32:12.84,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Can you wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.84,0:32:14.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His sister Natsuki has fallen silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.58,0:32:17.91,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Can you wait, Natsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.91,0:32:21.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Even though he wasn't asked Hideki has decided to purchase rice balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.15,0:32:23.09,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,It's fine here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.72,0:32:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it fine here?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.09,0:32:23.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's a shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.92,0:32:27.02,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,They will have rice balls and dango, {\alphaFF\t(2624,2624,\alpha0)}you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.02,0:32:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be looking after her, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.36,0:32:32.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Natsuki is not getting off.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.30,0:32:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Your brother will be back soon, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.27,0:32:38.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Natsuki and an old guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.84,0:32:41.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Only today she has no major problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.94,0:32:50.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hideki why are you worried about rice balls at this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.48,0:32:55.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,If you don't hurry then Natsuki will cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.46,0:33:01.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The driver thought of a topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.12,0:33:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(5464,0,\alphaFF)}The brother talked about a baby. It would be nice if it was a girl, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.86,0:33:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Then both of you will be able to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.30,0:33:13.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's answering a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.60,0:33:16.44,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.44,0:33:21.51,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Where do you have bald?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.51,0:33:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What? Ah, rice balls?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.88,0:33:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have any rice balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.65,0:33:28.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They don't have rice balls?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.42,0:33:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it about to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.59,0:33:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Still? {\alphaFF\t(1655,1655,\alpha0)}Still?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.06,0:33:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.99,0:33:39.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He can't stand it here and there.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.13,0:33:42.30,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,My mother {\alphaFF\t(1555,1555,\alpha0)}is about to give birth
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.30,0:33:44.57,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,to a baby
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.57,0:33:46.50,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,and her breasts
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.50,0:33:50.44,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,need to produce milk
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.44,0:33:52.18,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,so I am here to purchase bald.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.28,0:33:56.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's why he's looking for "bald".
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.28,0:33:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\pos(694.285,58.22)}TN: Imitating Hideki he calls them bald on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.11,0:33:57.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hideki is kind after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.78,0:34:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.78,0:34:01.22,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,For the baby
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.22,0:34:03.12,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,milk will come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.12,0:34:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,From the breasts...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.12,0:34:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,She will eat it {\alphaFF\t(1424,1424,\alpha0)}to produce breast milk, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.36,0:34:10.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hideki has learned that
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.29,0:34:12.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,when Natsuki was still a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.76,0:34:15.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's what his mother would often say while eating rice balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.33,0:34:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Will daifuku do?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.33,0:34:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(678.857,74.237)\fs45}Rice cake stuffed with bean jam
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.00,0:34:21.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Daifuku. They share the mochi and anko qualities.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.97,0:34:24.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He decided to get daifuku instead of rice balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.78,0:34:30.61,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Ah... mh... did.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.61,0:34:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy did? Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.72,0:34:34.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Natsuki started talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.02,0:34:39.26,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Papa called on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.26,0:34:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see. {\alphaFF\t(2186,2186,\alpha0)}That's what he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.53,0:34:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand it that well.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.26,0:34:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll be 306 yen please.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.03,0:34:51.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Alright hurry. You got the daifuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.97,0:34:55.91,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I will splish-splash.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.91,0:34:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you splash? {\alphaFF\t(2019,2019,\alpha0)}The pool?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.01,0:35:01.31,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,{\t(3022,0,\alphaFF)\pos(720,999)}The bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.04,0:35:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(1992,0,\alphaFF)}The bath? I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.31,0:35:03.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's able to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.35,0:35:05.95,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Will you take a bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.95,0:35:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(2656,0,\alphaFF)}I might also{\alphaFF\t(1088,1088,\alpha0)}{\t(2656,0,\alphaFF)} take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.12,0:35:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(4125,0,\alphaFF)}When I sweat{\alphaFF\t(1389,1389,\alpha0)}{\t(4125,0,\alphaFF)} or before sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.63,0:35:18.63,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Did you take one?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.63,0:35:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Today?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.13,0:35:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(2523,0,\alphaFF)}I haven't taken one yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.10,0:35:25.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,How nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.77,0:35:27.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,While Hideki went shopping
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.57,0:35:32.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,the old guy and Natsuki were exchanging pleasantries.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.81,0:35:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.08,0:35:38.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hideki doesn't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.78,0:35:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Since your brother wants to get on can you move this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.95,0:35:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Since he...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.62,0:35:46.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,If the guy says so.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.02,0:35:49.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The purchase has been made. Better hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.66,0:35:52.03,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,It will say Shouji Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.03,0:35:55.67,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,on the sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.30,0:35:58.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Their father in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.27,0:36:04.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.41,0:36:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. Around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.55,0:36:10.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is Shouji Hospital.
