Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.48,0:51:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(2989,0,\alphaFF)}The monsters. {\alphaFF\t(1254,1254,\alpha0)\t(2989,0,\alphaFF)}It's calling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.88,0:51:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No no no. It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.58,0:51:16.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,So he can speak with the monster over the phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.82,0:51:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Touri, do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.89,0:51:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's defeat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.12,0:51:22.52,Studio,,0,0,0,,- What's up with the pretend.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.56,0:51:23.99,Studio,,0,0,0,,- He's pretending so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.72,0:51:23.23,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,{\t(1226,0,\alphaFF)\pos(720,996.2)}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.23,0:51:26.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Dad, please defeat the monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.69,0:51:27.36,Studio,,0,0,0,,- What was that.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.49,0:51:27.36,Studio,,0,0,0,,- A phone call from the monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.46,0:51:30.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Running at full speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.07,0:51:36.67,Studio,,0,0,0,,Alright. He's off.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.94,0:51:41.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Dad, isn't there something you must do?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.08,0:51:43.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,You better go fight the monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.95,0:51:49.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,If he can get past the first intersection, he's all set, dad explained.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.22,0:51:57.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We beg of you, Touri. {\alphaFF\t(1758,1758,\alpha0)}Please go for real this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.83,0:51:58.56,Studio,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.10,0:52:03.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He crossed.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.33,0:52:04.60,Studio,,0,0,0,,He's so great. He will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.90,0:52:08.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He finally left.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.87,0:52:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(411.6,945)}Who does Touri ressemble?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.37,0:52:12.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Touri, does he resemble his dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.41,0:52:13.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Or his mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.98,0:52:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.64,0:52:16.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Which part?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.05,0:52:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He can do it but {\alphaFF\t(2853,2853,\alpha0)}he doesn't have the courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.42,0:52:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Like with me he will worry: {\alphaFF\t(2621,2621,\alpha0)}Will I be fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.03,0:52:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's getting dark outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.76,0:52:33.76,Studio,,0,0,0,,It really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.26,0:52:35.73,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In no time the sun has set and it's approaching twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.73,0:52:39.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Surely they are worried if Touri is doing fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.30,0:52:42.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But he seems to remember the directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.14,0:52:45.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And crossing the street properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.57,0:52:46.57,Studio,,0,0,0,,He really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.57,0:52:51.05,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,{\t(3863,0,\alphaFF)}I don't know {\alphaFF\t(2028,2028,\alpha0)\t(3863,0,\alphaFF)}the name of the meats.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.18,0:52:56.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He doesn't know, yeah. His dad's order is too complex.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.25,0:52:56.02,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,{\alphaFF\t(0,320,\alpha50)\pos(720,996.2)\t(2188,0,\alphaFF)}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.99,0:53:01.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Salted tongue, basil marinated chicken neck and extremely spicy intestines.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.36,0:53:04.73,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Though he doesn't remember he enters the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.73,0:53:06.73,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What will he do?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.56,0:53:11.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,At the entrance there is a wall of autographs from patrons.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.67,0:53:14.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His father is also a regular customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.77,0:53:18.47,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,What type of meat do you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.01,0:53:18.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He could also do it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.91,0:53:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you come to buy meat?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.78,0:53:24.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He intends to make the waiter cite all the types of meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.85,0:53:26.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,If he hears it he will remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.55,0:53:29.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Will he notice the three options in between?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.89,0:53:33.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The assistant manager who knows his dad well came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.46,0:53:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I will start with the ones that your papa likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.42,0:53:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's one of those then say "yeah", okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.03,0:53:41.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's starting now.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.36,0:54:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1155.086,740.956)}Salted tongue
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.36,0:54:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1158.515,906.013)}Basil marinated\N chicken neck
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.36,0:54:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1155.086,1033.549)}Extremely spicy\Ninstestines
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.20,0:53:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he mention "Basil marinated chicken neck?"
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.87,0:53:45.07,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,He did.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.07,0:53:46.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He got the first one right.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.10,0:53:48.10,Studio,,0,0,0,,Alright. Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.34,0:53:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And then what else...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.04,0:53:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What about marinated ribs?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.31,0:53:55.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's a pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.14,0:53:57.14,Studio,,0,0,0,,He didn't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.28,0:53:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And your father likes salted tongue. Did he bring that up?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.75,0:54:01.22,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,He did.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.78,0:54:03.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A splendid hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.39,0:54:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still more?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.02,0:54:05.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The last one is difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.82,0:54:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it sweet? {\alphaFF\t(1891,1891,\alpha0)}Or spicy? Do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.22,0:54:10.69,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,It's spicy.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.69,0:54:11.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Great piece of info.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.79,0:54:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.16,0:54:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's something your dad likes then... {\alphaFF\t(3060,3060,\alpha0)}intestines?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.03,0:54:20.40,Studio,,0,0,0,,He did say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.40,0:54:22.30,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,He said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.07,0:54:22.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,How splendid.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.30,0:54:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.61,0:54:25.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He got them all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.41,0:54:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,For how many people?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.38,0:54:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So you want 5 of each?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.75,0:54:32.21,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.05,0:54:33.68,Studio,,0,0,0,,He was able to get it out of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.21,0:54:34.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He remembered the amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.12,0:54:39.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's getting 5 of each so they are preparing food for 15 people.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.49,0:54:40.79,Studio,,0,0,0,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.92,0:54:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Touri, do you want to have a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.16,0:54:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You really did well.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.53,0:54:45.53,Studio,,0,0,0,,He really did.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.89,0:54:47.53,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,He said that there's a {\alphaFF\t(2093,2093,\alpha0)}monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.53,0:54:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a monster? {\alphaFF\t(2423,2423,\alpha0)}At home?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.06,0:54:52.20,Studio,,0,0,0,,{\pos(225,72.712)}- There's a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.57,0:54:53.37,Studio,,0,0,0,,{\pos(223.286,143.644)}- The scare worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.30,0:54:56.17,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Papa will beat up the monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.47,0:54:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He will beat up the monster? Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.94,0:54:59.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was able to grasp the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.47,0:55:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.11,0:55:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Since papa is fighting him then Touri also needs to do his best.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.35,0:55:05.88,Studio,,0,0,0,,He's so great a peptalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.38,0:55:07.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's done cooking now.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.08,0:55:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful. See you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.95,0:55:12.75,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,See you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.92,0:55:14.96,Studio,,0,0,0,,How great. He's a nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.79,0:55:14.46,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.46,0:55:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.59,0:55:17.93,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,{\t(2057,0,\alphaFF)}I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.40,0:55:25.23,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,It started raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.50,0:55:32.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The rain became more intense. Hurry up and get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.24,0:55:35.38,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,I must buy cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.38,0:55:37.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Oh that's right. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.15,0:55:39.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His father asked him to do it as a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.15,0:55:42.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,For his mother and the baby she's carrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.28,0:55:43.19,Studio,,0,0,0,,How nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.19,0:55:45.32,Studio,,0,0,0,,He better go.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.39,0:55:48.82,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,I will leave it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.82,0:55:51.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His raincoat is drenched from the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.23,0:55:55.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Thinking it would be bad to drip in the shop. What a good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.49,0:55:55.03,Studio,,0,0,0,,{\pos(228,89)}He's so thoughtful.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.63,0:55:58.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's only bringing in the wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.50,0:56:05.51,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,{\t(2695,0,\alphaFF)\pos(720,1001)}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.50,0:56:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(2695,0,\alphaFF)}Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.14,0:56:07.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.54,0:56:10.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He forgot what type of cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.75,0:56:12.21,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,What was it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.21,0:56:16.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Touri needs to psyche himself up for the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.25,0:56:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.92,0:56:18.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Without being prepared...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.79,0:56:21.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,the shop door opened up to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.92,0:56:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you come to buy a cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.23,0:56:25.29,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.29,0:56:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you come to buy?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.16,0:56:27.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.80,0:56:31.47,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Short cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.70,0:56:31.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He suddenly remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.47,0:56:33.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The sweet and sour strawberry cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.47,0:56:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Who will eat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.94,0:56:36.04,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.54,0:56:41.51,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Because she said that she's nauseous...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.51,0:56:44.05,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,so she wants something sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.05,0:56:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Can she eat cake despite not feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.58,0:56:48.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But she's not actually sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.32,0:56:49.92,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.82,0:56:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So she's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.65,0:56:54.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The lady totally thinks that she's sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.65,0:56:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\pos(652.5,59)}TN (written): Mama, hurry up and be well. From Touri.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.99,0:56:58.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He noticed something.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.76,0:57:00.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.20,0:57:03.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The flowers his dad mentioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.63,0:57:06.64,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,I will buy this.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.64,0:57:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.30,0:57:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called preserved flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.17,0:57:12.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Flowers that don't wilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.91,0:57:17.58,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,{\t(4390,0,\alphaFF)}Since she's carrying a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.08,0:57:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So you will be a brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.81,0:57:20.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.08,0:57:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom will appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.65,0:57:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I will put it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.35,0:57:27.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,"I will be a big brother."
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.12,0:57:31.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He is able to properly say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.54,0:57:45.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,While it's all dark
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.94,0:57:48.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,he can still see his father and mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.61,0:57:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.88,0:57:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Touri.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.42,0:57:56.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Touri isn't crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.69,0:58:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Touri.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.29,0:58:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Touri.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.93,0:58:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You are so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.56,0:58:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay? Is it not heavy?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.43,0:58:10.50,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.50,0:58:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.07,0:58:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.60,0:58:17.87,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,I bought the cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.87,0:58:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.31,0:58:24.75,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,I bought it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.75,0:58:28.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The goal is his baby that his mother is carrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.02,0:58:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(2119,0,\alphaFF)}You've become a big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.19,0:58:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(1426,0,\alphaFF)}You bought it all?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.33,0:58:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.56,0:58:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There's some in this one too?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.06,0:58:44.60,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Mama, {\alphaFF\t(1092,1092,\alpha0)}flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.60,0:58:47.34,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,I also bought flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.20,0:58:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.34,0:58:49.67,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,{\t(2052,0,\alphaFF)}At the cake shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.81,0:58:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How admirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.94,0:58:57.68,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,When the baby is born
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.68,0:59:00.92,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,both you and the baby can use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.22,0:59:04.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,No one taught him to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.29,0:59:06.09,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Please use it for decoration.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.49,0:59:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hug me tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.56,0:59:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.53,0:59:16.30,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.53,0:59:16.30,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.30,0:59:19.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His two big brothers have come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.13,0:59:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He was succesful in his errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.20,0:59:23.31,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\t(826,0,\alphaFF)}Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.87,0:59:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(2156,0,\alphaFF)\pos(718.8,1002.6)}Look. He bought all this.
