Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.70,1:01:04.97,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Mischievous {\alphaFF\t(4423,4423,\alpha0)}rascal {\alphaFF\t(6725,6725,\alpha0)}but cute.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.84,1:01:04.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,999.4)}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.97,1:01:07.78,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,{\alphaFF\t(0,359,\alpha0)}A boy you want to spoil.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.78,1:01:11.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,So he's exactly like Touri was back then.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.95,1:01:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like your big brother?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.01,1:01:13.75,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.75,1:01:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like Touri?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.68,1:01:15.18,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.18,1:01:16.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He can't stand still.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.35,1:01:21.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The mother spends her days laughing and scolding.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.56,1:01:24.63,BlueFill,,0,0,0,,{\alphaFF\t(0,318,\alpha0)\t(2787,0,\alphaFF)\fs40\pos(295.8,825.8)}Oldest son \NAito (Middle School 3rd year)
