Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.64,1:01:37.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And about dad?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.27,1:01:42.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Might be heartbroken the day they will finally spread their wings.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.38,1:01:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alphaFF\t(0,487,\alpha0)\t(4525,0,\alphaFF)\fs50\pos(319.5,253)}Nagano ● Ooshikamura
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.48,1:01:48.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This Spanish mama has lived in Japan since she was 5.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.45,1:01:52.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And now she has a cafe at Ooshikamura.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.72,1:01:57.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The interior design is made by the musician papa.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.86,1:01:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it there. The tea.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.59,1:02:00.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Taiyou, who's only been allowed to wipe tables.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.16,1:02:05.10,BlueFill,,0,0,0,,{\pos(382.8,439.4)\alphaFF\t(0,490,\alpha0)\t(4527,0,\alphaFF)\fs40}Taiyou [means Sun]\N3 years 2 months
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.63,1:02:05.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since he turned 3 years he has been asked to serve the customers.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.47,1:02:07.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He did it. His first time doing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.67,1:02:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I will go get it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.94,1:02:12.34,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Will you eat sweets today?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.61,1:02:12.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He can even take their orders.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.34,1:02:15.51,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Corn and... Corn and...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.68,1:02:18.85,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,we have soup pulp donuts.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.98,1:02:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Soy pulp (okara) donuts?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.85,1:02:20.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They understood from the "soup pulp".
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.85,1:02:24.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Soy pulp (okara) is healthy and a popular menu item.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.32,1:02:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, listen. About the soy pulp...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.19,1:02:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(202.8,993)\alphaFF\t(0,317,\alpha0)\t(4288,0,\alphaFF)}Filmed in 2013.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.56,1:02:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,we've run out but...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.13,1:02:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,we will make more okara donuts.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.43,1:02:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Taiyou, go and shop.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.33,1:02:36.43,Studio,,0,0,0,,Did he get it?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.50,1:02:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,At the tofu shop say: {\alphaFF\t(1186,1186,\alpha0)}"Okara, please."
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.63,1:02:39.93,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,By car.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.93,1:02:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Not by car. By foot.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.20,1:02:42.17,Studio,,0,0,0,,He wants to go by car.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.17,1:02:44.17,Studio,,0,0,0,,Not by car.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.27,1:02:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you do it?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.90,1:02:43.64,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.64,1:02:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,When you go out...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.01,1:02:45.37,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,An insect!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.71,1:02:47.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Is he listening properly?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.81,1:02:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,When you finish shopping...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.27,1:02:48.31,Studio,,0,0,0,,Is he listening?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.51,1:02:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,At the agricultural cooperative...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.38,1:02:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to make salad today{\alphaFF\t(2087,2087,\alpha0)} so get some Chinese cabbage.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.95,1:02:55.52,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.45,1:02:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure? Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.78,1:02:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,After you buy it you can also buy {\alphaFF\t(1159,1159,\alpha0)}your favorite candy.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.62,1:03:01.12,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep-did-it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.46,1:03:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Smooch.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.19,1:03:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. Off you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.09,1:03:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.63,1:03:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.56,1:03:09.83,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.13,1:03:12.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's going on his errand on a high note.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.10,1:03:24.08,WhiteRedBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(741.6,586.6)\alphaFF\t(0,321,\alpha0)}Home
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.10,1:03:24.08,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\alphaFF\t(0,321,\alpha0)\pos(1237.2,519.4)}Toufu shop
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.10,1:03:24.08,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\alphaFF\t(0,321,\alpha0)\pos(211.2,114.6)}Agricultural\N cooperative
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.70,1:03:16.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,At the tofu shop used by everyone at Ooshikamura
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.10,1:03:18.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,the okara is said to be different.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.10,1:03:19.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Perfect for donuts.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.87,1:03:26.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,At the agricultural cooperative on the way back he is asked to get Chinese cabbage.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.31,1:03:25.55,Studio,,0,0,0,,Will he be fine?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.35,1:03:29.35,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.35,1:03:31.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He just left the house.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.02,1:03:33.19,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Just a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.19,1:03:35.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There's still a lot to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.49,1:03:37.96,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Just a bit more. {\alphaFF\t(1656,1656,\alpha0)}Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.96,1:03:39.19,Studio,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.19,1:03:41.19,Studio,,0,0,0,,Is he fine?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.03,1:03:42.50,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Meimei's flowers {\alphaFF\t(1454,1454,\alpha0)}were here.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.50,1:03:43.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's not a goat.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.07,1:03:45.80,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I will give it to Meimei.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.80,1:03:47.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His mothers' name is Mei.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.87,1:03:51.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Will his mother even be delighted by these leaves?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.04,1:03:55.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Arriving at the highly regarded Minoya tofu shop.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.51,1:04:00.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's not getting tofu, though.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.32,1:04:02.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's supposed to say "okara, please".
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.62,1:04:04.69,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\t(1920,0,\alphaFF)}Here.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.75,1:04:08.29,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,We are making soup pulp donuts so...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.29,1:04:10.29,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,please.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.29,1:04:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.96,1:04:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.53,1:04:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.46,1:04:18.13,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Soup pulp.. donuts, we are making it
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.77,1:04:21.44,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I was told to get soup pulp.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.27,1:04:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you... donuts?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.54,1:04:26.21,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.21,1:04:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.31,1:04:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.04,1:04:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mom is making her famous {\alphaFF\t(1091,1091,\alpha0)}soy pulp (okara) donuts.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.15,1:04:33.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She understood him.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.48,1:04:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They are right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.22,1:04:35.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's 50 yen per bag.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.75,1:04:38.05,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,This?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.48,1:04:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this one.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.05,1:04:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Will this do? {\alphaFF\t(1192,1192,\alpha0)}Just one?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.19,1:04:40.92,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(717,1001)}Um, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.92,1:04:44.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He has seen the donuts before but never the ingredients.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.66,1:04:46.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,"Is this really soup pulp?" He wonders.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.43,1:04:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Is all fine?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.06,1:04:48.63,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I can go.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.63,1:04:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.16,1:04:52.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He didn't even put it in the basket  that he brought all the way here.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.07,1:04:54.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Next is the Chinese cabbage.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.17,1:04:54.97,Studio,,0,0,0,,{\pos(229.5,75)}Put it in the basket.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.97,1:04:57.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Oh no, he's heading straight home.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.94,1:05:00.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He must be worried if he got the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.01,1:05:03.14,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,They said that this is soup pulp.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.14,1:05:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Soup pulp?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.34,1:05:05.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,An old lady from the neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.01,1:05:05.05,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Soy pulp.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.05,1:05:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Otera (temple)?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.98,1:05:07.88,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Okara (soup pulp).
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.88,1:05:08.78,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Otara.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.02,1:05:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.59,1:05:12.42,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,They said that this is it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.42,1:05:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They told you this is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.72,1:05:15.32,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,They said "otara".
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.39,1:05:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,O-ka-ra.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.32,1:05:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. You did well.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.03,1:05:20.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What? It was really this thing?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.36,1:05:22.33,Studio,,0,0,0,,I did it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.26,1:05:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you forgot one thing. {\alphaFF\t(2292,2292,\alpha0)}What was it?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.33,1:05:25.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The Chinese cabbage.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.30,1:05:26.53,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,This.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.53,1:05:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, for Meimei? Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.24,1:05:29.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Huh? She was pleased.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.54,1:05:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.07,1:05:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,At the agricultural cooperative what was it that you needed?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.61,1:05:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What type of vegetable?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.78,1:05:40.28,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Vegdable.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.75,1:05:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, which one?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.28,1:05:41.08,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Vegdable
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.08,1:05:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Want me to teach you? {\alphaFF\t(1592,1592,\alpha0)}Chinese cabbage.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.72,1:05:45.75,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Chinese cabbage.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.75,1:05:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Chinese cabbage.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.75,1:05:47.76,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Chinese cabbage.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.52,1:05:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Chinese cabbage.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.76,1:05:49.59,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Chinese cabbage, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.59,1:05:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.09,1:05:52.16,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.83,1:05:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Off you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.83,1:05:53.80,Studio,,0,0,0,,- Did he really? \N - Really?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.16,1:05:54.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's leaving once again on a high note.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.16,1:05:56.40,Studio,,0,0,0,,It's a worry.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.43,1:05:56.70,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,With the okara...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.70,1:05:57.93,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,With the okara...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.93,1:06:01.17,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and make donuts.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.17,1:06:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make them together later.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.60,1:06:04.54,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Yes, {\alphaFF\t(926,926,\alpha0)}I did it!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.81,1:06:09.98,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Today Taiyou {\alphaFF\t(1486,1486,\alpha0)}is shopping.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.35,1:06:12.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He came out on the big street.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.35,1:06:14.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Look at his game face.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.18,1:06:17.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He needs to cross at this crossing.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.55,1:06:17.85,Studio,,0,0,0,,What a serious face.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.25,1:06:19.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He trained so many times with his mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.62,1:06:22.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,However he passed it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.89,1:06:23.89,Studio,,0,0,0,,- Huh? What? \N - The other way.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.56,1:06:24.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The agricultural cooperative is on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.89,1:06:28.33,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I should go over there.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.33,1:06:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to cross?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.36,1:06:30.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's the cameraman.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.37,1:06:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you should cross at this crossing.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.70,1:06:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Over there where people cross.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.14,1:06:41.98,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\t(5524,0,\alphaFF)}Ah, it's people!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.17,1:06:39.47,Studio,,0,0,0,,It's people!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.94,1:06:42.28,Studio,,0,0,0,,He realized midway.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.28,1:06:44.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Even a 3 year old person can cross there.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.61,1:06:47.15,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I will cross.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.89,1:06:53.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He has arrived at the cooperative agricultural supermarket.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.36,1:06:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.42,1:06:57.73,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.69,1:06:59.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Chinese cabbage, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.76,1:07:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You came back.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.96,1:07:03.96,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.03,1:07:09.94,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Meimei told me to buy vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.74,1:07:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.94,1:07:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Which vegetable?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.31,1:07:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the vegetables and have a look.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.27,1:07:15.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Going to the vegetable corner.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.38,1:07:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one, I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.48,1:07:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This one. Cabbage?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.68,1:07:20.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's not cabbage.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.66,1:07:20.72,Studio,,0,0,0,,It's different.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.68,1:07:24.09,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,She said "vegetable".
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.68,1:07:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pickle.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.22,1:07:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder exactly what your mother said.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.49,1:07:27.42,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Vegetable.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.42,1:07:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pickle.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.62,1:07:29.89,Studio,,0,0,0,,Vegetable.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.12,1:07:31.63,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.63,1:07:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This is mizuna.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.99,1:07:34.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's not mizuna.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.36,1:07:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Green onion.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.13,1:07:36.53,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's not green onion.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.53,1:07:38.80,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Is this pumpkin?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.67,1:07:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Pumpkin.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.80,1:07:40.33,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Tomato.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.40,1:07:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, tomato.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.33,1:07:42.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's not pumpkin nor tomatoes.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.84,1:07:43.50,Studio,,0,0,0,,What was it?\N It's right there.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.70,1:07:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This is daikon.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.07,1:07:45.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,So close!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.21,1:07:46.24,Studio,,0,0,0,,Below it. Below it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.27,1:07:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Chinese cabbage.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.31,1:07:46.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.97,1:07:48.44,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,And this one is daikon.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.44,1:07:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's also daikon.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.94,1:07:52.61,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,This is mandarin.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.08,1:07:52.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He skipped it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.61,1:07:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You know so much. It's mandarin.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.12,1:07:57.89,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,You don't have vegetables?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.89,1:08:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We do. Which one are you here for?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.45,1:08:02.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They went to the vegetables because of him.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.19,1:08:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it Chinese cabbage?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.96,1:08:05.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Though it's right in front of his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.66,1:08:06.73,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.73,1:08:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.20,1:08:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back to your mother and ask: {\alphaFF\t(1852,1852,\alpha0)}"Which vegetable was it again?"
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.73,1:08:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you don't know go back and ask.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.10,1:08:17.71,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.91,1:08:21.94,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\t(3720,0,\alphaFF)}What vegetable did she say?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.84,1:08:26.71,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,What type of vegetable.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.25,1:08:29.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He couldn't buy vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.32,1:08:32.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Even though his mother was looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.85,1:08:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.{\alphaFF\t(1059,1059,\alpha0)} Did you buy it?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.69,1:08:36.69,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,What type of vegetable was it?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.69,1:08:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You forgot? Did you say it right?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.06,1:08:41.76,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Vegetable.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.76,1:08:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Chinese cabbage.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.76,1:08:44.20,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Chinese cabbage.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.30,1:08:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Chinese cabbage.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.20,1:08:47.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His mother got an idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.27,1:08:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Taiyou, how old are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.14,1:08:51.87,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,3 years old [san sai].
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.97,1:08:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right 3 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.87,1:08:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And you should get? {\alphaFF\t(758,758,\alpha0)}Chinese cabbage [hakusai].
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.58,1:08:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Say it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.74,1:08:57.58,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,100 years old [hyakusai].
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.74,1:08:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Say it once more.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.58,1:08:59.01,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Chinese cabbage.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.25,1:08:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Once more.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.01,1:08:59.68,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Chinese cabbage.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.88,1:09:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Once more.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.58,1:09:04.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Whether it's 100 years [hyakusai] or Chinese cabbage [hakusai] I'm sure they will understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.55,1:09:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,100 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.19,1:09:05.99,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Chinese cabbage.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.09,1:09:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Taiyou, how old are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.16,1:09:08.29,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm 3 years old.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.29,1:09:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What type of vegetable will you buy?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.93,1:09:14.36,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Chinese cabbage.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.53,1:09:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.10,1:09:16.10,Studio,,0,0,0,,- What an amazing mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.36,1:09:16.13,Studio,,0,0,0,,- Amazing mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.13,1:09:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Basket. Basket. And the wallet too.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.10,1:09:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to buy?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.27,1:09:23.40,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\t(1521,0,\alphaFF)}Leafy vegetables [hayasai].
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.07,1:09:25.41,Studio,,0,0,0,,He turned it into leafy vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.70,1:09:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Chinese cabbage.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.67,1:09:26.27,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Chinese cabbage.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.17,1:09:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Repeat it on the way.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.27,1:09:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Chinese cabbage, Chinese cabbage, Chinese cabbage...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.98,1:09:30.41,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Chinese cabbage. Chinese cabbage.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.31,1:09:31.88,Studio,,0,0,0,,That's right. While he still got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.88,1:09:34.85,Studio,,0,0,0,,- While he still remembers.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.05,1:09:34.85,Studio,,0,0,0,,- Keep saying it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.85,1:09:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, off you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.48,1:09:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.42,1:09:39.39,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.29,1:09:42.19,Studio,,0,0,0,,Don't mix it in.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.96,1:09:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Chinese cabbage.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.29,1:09:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Chinese cabbage. Chinese cabbage.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.16,1:09:47.90,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Chinese cabbage. Chinese cabbage.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.59,1:09:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Chinese cabbage.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.66,1:09:48.83,Studio,,0,0,0,,{\pos(235.5,75)}Go and say "Chinese cabbage".
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.30,1:09:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. Off you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.14,1:09:57.21,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Chinese cabbage. {\alphaFF\t(985,985,\alpha0)}Chinese cabbage.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.57,1:09:59.14,Studio,,0,0,0,,That's so good.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.21,1:09:59.37,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Almost Chinese cabbage. [As in: almost 100 years old]
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.37,1:10:00.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's the spirit.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.84,1:10:03.31,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Chinese cabbage. Chinese cabbage.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.38,1:10:05.78,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,, Chinese cabbage.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.61,1:10:08.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This time it will surely be fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.98,1:10:11.82,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Taiyou is 3 years old.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.82,1:10:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,3 years?{\alphaFF\t(1689,1689,\alpha0)} What a good boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.69,1:10:19.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And then... what age?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.03,1:10:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you go and ask?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.36,1:10:24.60,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,She said Chinese cabbage.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.67,1:10:26.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He did it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.67,1:10:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Chinese cabbage.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.54,1:10:32.21,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Is it really Chinese cabbage?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.94,1:10:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.21,1:10:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Since this is Chinese cabbage.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.64,1:10:36.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,So this is what Chinese cabbage looks like.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.98,1:10:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How great that you went and asked.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.78,1:10:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a good boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.85,1:10:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you carry it?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.71,1:10:42.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This time he puts it in the basket.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.52,1:10:45.39,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Chinese cabbage. {\alphaFF\t(885,885,\alpha0)}Chinese cabbage.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.82,1:10:50.09,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Chinese cabbage is @#!?&...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.09,1:10:51.89,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Yahoo.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.46,1:10:54.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.00,1:11:00.10,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Chinese cabbage. {\alphaFF\t(1654,1654,\alpha0)}Chinese cabbage.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.67,1:11:03.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,No matter his age in the future he will never forget: Chinese cabbage
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.14,1:11:05.84,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Chinese cabbage.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.84,1:11:09.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ah! The lady who helped him cross the street.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.24,1:11:12.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He exchanged glances with the cameraman.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.38,1:11:14.12,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,How old are you now?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.25,1:11:17.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Come on. Tell the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.75,1:11:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.46,1:11:23.46,Studio,,0,0,0,,Can't tell him.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.09,1:11:26.66,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Taiyou is 3 years old.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.46,1:11:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You are 3 years old?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.66,1:11:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You are not 100 years old?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.63,1:11:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't your mother waiting?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.03,1:11:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It will get dark. Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.27,1:11:35.77,Studio,,0,0,0,,So cute.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.94,1:11:39.44,Studio,,0,0,0,,He's such a cute kid. Just the best.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.44,1:11:42.24,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I brought it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.58,1:11:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it? All by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.78,1:11:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You are amazing, Taiyou.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.48,1:11:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You bought this?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.58,1:11:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it called?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.42,1:11:51.82,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Chinese cabbage.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.65,1:11:54.42,Studio,,0,0,0,,So cute.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.42,1:11:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You are amazing. Give me a smooch.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.26,1:12:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Your favorite {\alphaFF\t(1090,1090,\alpha0)}Chinese cabbage salad.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.16,1:12:05.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shredding the cabbage and sprinkling some Katsuobushi​ on top.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.47,1:12:08.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Then add sesame oil and soy sauce and it's done.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.07,1:12:10.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Memei's specialty: Chinese cabbage salad.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.20,1:12:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Bon apetit.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.84,1:12:14.61,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Meimei.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.61,1:12:17.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Does it suit the taste of a 3 year old?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.08,1:12:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Taiyou is it tasty?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.45,1:12:19.51,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Tasty.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.85,1:12:23.62,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Meimei, you should eat too.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.62,1:12:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I might eat later.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.62,1:12:29.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As long as you eat this you might get to live to 100 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.59,1:12:31.86,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\t(1957,0,\alphaFF)}It might be gone by then.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.16,1:12:39.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As the cold gains pace by the day
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.23,1:12:41.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,the autumn colors have appeared
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.71,1:12:46.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's the height of the autumn colors.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.77,1:12:49.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In this town a girl was born.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.18,1:12:55.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since she is autumn colored and makes everyone happy they called her Kureha [autumn colors].
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.24,1:12:55.88,PurpleFill,,0,0,0,,{\alphaFF\t(0,357,\alpha0)\t(7297,0,\alphaFF)\pos(448.8,834.6)}Kureha \N{\fs30}[Autumn colors]
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.15,1:12:59.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She always sticks to her mother and is such a cuddled baby girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.72,1:13:04.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But when Kureha turned 2 \Nher mother was hospitalized.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.43,1:13:06.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It was cervical cancer​.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.26,1:13:09.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Her mother rarely came back home.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.66,1:13:12.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And in no time she turned into a well-behaved child.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.47,1:13:15.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,"I don't want to be a burden on mother"....
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.60,1:13:18.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,she suddenly said when she turned 4.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.41,1:13:21.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,"Mama, if you want me over, just tell me. I'll be right there."
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.74,1:13:25.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kureha has said that she can ride the bus and go by herself.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.45,1:13:26.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,"We will make Kureha do it"
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.95,1:13:30.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,her mother said while thinking up an errand.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.02,1:13:33.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But it won't be an easy one.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.09,1:13:35.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is the father.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.22,1:13:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1204.8,994.6)\alphaFF\t(0,324,\alpha0)\t(5229,0,\alphaFF)\fs40}Filmed in 2013.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.49,1:13:38.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He has passed 58 years by a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.09,1:13:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a leftover.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.26,1:13:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They are all over each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.47,1:13:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And normally
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.80,1:13:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alphaFF\t(0,155,\alpha0)}because of doting on her {\alphaFF\t(2024,2157,\alpha0)}he ends up buying her anything she desires.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.74,1:13:54.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Working hard as a truck driver.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.94,1:13:58.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He has to since had his first daughter late in life.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.85,1:14:02.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Even the big brother has started to worry about her.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.68,1:14:06.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She knows it will be tough but she wants her to do her best.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.25,1:14:08.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's why she's writing her a letter.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.66,1:14:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alphaFF\t(0,184,\alpha0)}As long as papa believes that Kureha will be fine
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.53,1:14:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and he can convey it then {\alphaFF\t(3088,3088,\alpha0)}Kureha will also say: "Alright".
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.24,1:14:24.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The father decided to make her bring her onigiri.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.84,1:14:28.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kureha is preparing various things on her own.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.11,1:14:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.41,1:14:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You should give it to the bus driver.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.08,1:14:33.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She will go by bus.s
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.41,1:14:36.32,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,This won't be enough, though.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.75,1:14:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It is enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.78,1:14:38.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They are using the town-loop bus.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.95,1:14:40.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It comes once an hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.65,1:14:43.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There's 26 minutes until the next bus.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.62,1:14:45.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.26,1:14:46.76,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,{\alphaFF\t(0,321,\alpha0)}I want to go with papa.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.09,1:14:49.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Despite having resolved that she will go by herself.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.93,1:14:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Then put it in here.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.07,1:14:52.73,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Don't wanna.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.20,1:14:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama is waiting.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.60,1:14:57.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Wonder what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.40,1:15:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama said {\alphaFF\t(2195,2195,\alpha0)}if Kureha comes {\alphaFF\t(3396,3396,\alpha0)}then I will feel better.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.94,1:15:06.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But she wants to go with papa after all.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.28,1:15:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Kureha, please go.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.82,1:15:11.69,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,But I can't go by myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.69,1:15:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes you can. {\alphaFF\t(1451,1451,\alpha0)}If it's you, Kureha, then you can do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.52,1:15:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.99,1:15:19.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kureha who knows how to get her way.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.66,1:15:22.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is where he usually caves in and buys her a toy.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.60,1:15:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. Since it's you, Kureha, then you can do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.83,1:15:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here. I will hug you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.80,1:15:30.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A hug?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.51,1:15:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.28,1:15:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.32,1:15:47.32,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,But if papa doesn't come with then I will be lonely.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.32,1:15:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.46,1:15:53.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The more he hugs Kureha, the weaker she becomes.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.06,1:15:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,... Since it's dad, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.16,1:15:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to go to your mom?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.00,1:15:59.70,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,{\alphaFF\t(0,319,\alpha0)}I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.17,1:15:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,1005.8)}You do, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.70,1:16:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you better do your best.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.34,1:16:03.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Deep down she wants to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.07,1:16:04.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But her tears won't stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.34,1:16:07.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The bus will come by in a bit.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.58,1:16:10.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Maybe she changes her mind if they go outside?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.64,1:16:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, do your best.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.51,1:16:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.05,1:16:14.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.28,1:16:19.19,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,{\t(3627,0,\alphaFF)}I can't stop crying.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.98,1:16:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(1927,0,\alphaFF)\pos(720,997.8)}You can't stop crying?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.82,1:16:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.49,1:16:24.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Only a baby can't cease crying.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.26,1:16:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alphaFF\t(0,353,\alpha0)\t(2155,0,\alphaFF)}It's fine. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.69,1:16:29.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kureha is no longer a baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.57,1:16:35.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In the end she didn't get on this bus.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.30,1:16:37.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next bus is in one hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.64,1:16:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Drink a bit of water.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.77,1:16:42.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They go back to the house and start over.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.18,1:16:42.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.98,1:16:45.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's constantly carrying her around.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.45,1:16:46.91,Studio,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.38,1:16:48.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's even making her drink water. Though she's already 4 years old.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.98,1:16:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The phone is ringing.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.65,1:16:53.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The caller is the mom.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.39,1:16:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.56,1:16:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't constantly carrying her around, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.39,1:16:59.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's as if she can see inside the house.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.43,1:17:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa, you better pull yourself together.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.26,1:17:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Or Kureha won't leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.86,1:17:06.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The mother wants the father to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.87,1:17:08.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Not with kindness
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.94,1:17:11.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,but for him to know that love needs strictness too.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.64,1:17:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Toughen your heart. {\alphaFF\t(1555,1555,\alpha0)}Please.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.44,1:17:19.11,Studio,,0,0,0,,She's scolding him, the dad!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.11,1:17:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want me to read mama's letter?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.91,1:17:23.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The letter from before the errand.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.08,1:17:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really appreciative of {\alphaFF\t(3829,3829,\alpha0)}being able to watch {\alphaFF\t(5231,5231,\alpha0)}the growth and development {\alphaFF\t(7133,7133,\alpha0)}of Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.59,1:17:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? So you will go to your mom's by yourself. Right?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.73,1:17:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(9165,0,\alphaFF)}It's tough for Kureha {\alphaFF\t(1557,1557,\alpha0)\t(9165,0,\alphaFF)}and it's tough for papa {\alphaFF\t(3293,3293,\alpha0)\t(9165,0,\alphaFF)}who must send Kureha out of the house {\alphaFF\t(4627,4627,\alpha0\t(9165,0,\alphaFF))}on her own.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.47,1:17:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(9602,0,\alphaFF)}It's your first time riding a bus on your own{\alphaFF\t(3296,3296,\alpha0)\t(9602,0,\alphaFF)} however{\alphaFF\t(4830,4830,\alpha0)\t(9602,0,\alphaFF)} please pull yourself together.{\alphaFF\t(7200,7200,\alpha0)\t(9602,0,\alphaFF)}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.65,1:18:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama is saying{\alphaFF\t(1657,1657,\alpha0)} that she's waiting.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.29,1:18:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(3156,0,\alphaFF)}If Kureha doesn't go then she will be lonely.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.33,1:18:07.93,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I will go to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.23,1:18:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you ride the bus this time?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.56,1:18:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.60,1:18:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Kureha, you can do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.54,1:18:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.80,1:18:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.44,1:18:21.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He decided to take her to the bus stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.34,1:18:25.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He couldn't stop her tears.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.95,1:18:27.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But he's not carrying her.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.92,1:18:29.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He must toughen his resolve.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.55,1:18:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't run.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.46,1:18:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.79,1:18:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Kureha, you can do it. That's what mom said.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.16,1:18:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be fine. Alright.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.56,1:18:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.73,1:18:44.57,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Just carry me a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.57,1:18:47.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He wants to hold her tight but he fights the feeling.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.23,1:18:49.40,Studio,,0,0,0,,Do you best, dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.90,1:18:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Lift your spirits.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.07,1:18:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,High five.{\alphaFF\t(1022,1022,\alpha0)} High five.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.97,1:18:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best. Do your best. Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.74,1:18:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.01,1:19:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.76,1:19:09.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He has decided not to turn his face back.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.76,1:19:14.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He endures the desire to look back.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.60,1:19:18.73,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ah, she stopped crying.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.73,1:19:20.73,Studio,,0,0,0,,For real.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.40,1:19:26.81,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(396,221.8)\alphaFF\t(0,356,\alpha0)}Hospital
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.40,1:19:26.81,WhiteRedBorder,,0,0,0,,{\alphaFF\t(0,356,\alpha0)\pos(1321.2,578.6)}Home
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.83,1:19:22.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ride the bus for 10 minutes
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.40,1:19:24.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and the hospital will be right there.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.10,1:19:26.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's on an errand to cheer up her mom.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.21,1:19:29.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The bus arrived.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.84,1:19:33.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Her expression changed.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.25,1:19:34.25,Studio,,0,0,0,,For real.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.59,1:19:41.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Alright, confirm the destination.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.02,1:19:43.99,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Do you go to Chuuou Hospital?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.99,1:19:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we do.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.19,1:19:47.73,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ooh, she was able to say it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.59,1:19:50.00,Studio,,0,0,0,,Remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.33,1:19:53.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,To avoid missing her stop she rides behind the driver.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.96,1:19:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We are taking off. Please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.50,1:19:56.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The dad was right there!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.57,1:19:59.61,Studio,,0,0,0,,He's waving.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.01,1:20:00.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Even though Kureha can't see.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.27,1:20:04.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,For a moment the dad watches her go.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.65,1:20:11.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,10 minutes on the bus and it will stop right in front of the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.69,1:20:18.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The errand is onigiri that the father made and the cheer of Kureha's presence.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.76,1:20:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alphaFF\t(0,350,\alpha0)\t(4254,0,\alphaFF)\fs35\pos(120.9,1043.8)}Filmed in 2013
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.59,1:20:21.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The hospital is within sight.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.90,1:20:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Next is {\alphaFF\t(1185,1185,\alpha0)}Ina Chuuou Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.87,1:20:28.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Alright. Soon she will get to see her mom.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.34,1:20:31.37,Studio,,0,0,0,,Remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.84,1:20:32.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She can get hugs from her mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.51,1:20:34.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's been holding it in the entire time.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.78,1:20:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.35,1:20:43.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She has arrived at the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.35,1:20:48.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's her first time coming here by herself.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.59,1:20:50.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The hospital where her mother is.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.03,1:20:53.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Mom, she's coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.69,1:20:55.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kureha all by herself.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.53,1:20:59.70,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.87,1:20:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.03,1:21:03.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Though she doesn't know the nurses.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.97,1:21:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.61,1:21:06.81,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.64,1:21:10.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,If she turns here then it will be her mothers' hospital room.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.38,1:21:16.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Please knock gently.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.22,1:21:17.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She flew in the door.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.45,1:21:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.56,1:21:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.32,1:21:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you come by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.19,1:21:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.93,1:21:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And you will go home by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.56,1:21:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,How great.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.57,1:21:33.73,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She believed in her.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.47,1:21:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You did your best.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.90,1:21:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to take off your raincoat?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.70,1:21:38.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Take off the raincoat
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.74,1:21:40.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and get an embrace from your mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.44,1:21:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.91,1:21:45.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kureha noticed that the nurse is acting different from usual.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.71,1:21:47.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They are really calm.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:48.38,1:21:50.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's been a while with her mother
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.12,1:21:52.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But rather than embracing longingly
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.29,1:21:55.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,their conversation is as if they are back home.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.16,1:21:57.56,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,{\t(2119,0,\alphaFF)}I did it like you said.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.69,1:22:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You brought this? Halloween.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.03,1:22:02.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I brought it since mom requested it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.96,1:22:05.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's Halloween soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.47,1:22:09.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The mother has borrowed a picture book at the book corner in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.20,1:22:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But... he ate it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.61,1:22:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The apple...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.31,1:22:17.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There's so much the mother wants to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.91,1:22:19.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Reading a picture book out loud.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.48,1:22:21.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Talk about kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.28,1:22:22.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And eat onigiri.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.65,1:22:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,These are well made.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.19,1:22:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(3287,0,\alphaFF)}I get energized when Kureha comes.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.02,1:22:33.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And to energize Kureha
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.96,1:22:36.73,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's giving her a manicure.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.73,1:22:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.80,1:22:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Now wait a bit.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.14,1:22:46.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Time flies when you are having fun.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.11,1:22:48.98,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I will give you a letter.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.28,1:22:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you write a letter? {\alphaFF\t(1686,1686,\alpha0)}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.08,1:22:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kureha, did you write it?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.38,1:22:56.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She can write?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.32,1:23:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,| \ + [] Δ -| ' /\ | \ + [ Δ -| ' /\
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.66,1:23:03.49,Studio,,0,0,0,,What does it say?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.66,1:23:04.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She read it to her mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.46,1:23:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.26,1:23:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alphaFF\t(0,155,\alpha0)}You wrote: "I hope mama will get better soon."?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.93,1:23:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(2224,0,\alphaFF)}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.47,1:23:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Since Kureha came...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.77,1:23:15.70,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.70,1:23:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.27,1:23:17.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The mother
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.50,1:23:20.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,has decided not to cry in front of Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.11,1:23:22.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,If she does then it will weaken Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.88,1:23:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a letter.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.01,1:23:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,When you get back home {\alphaFF\t(1691,1691,\alpha0)}have papa read it for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.82,1:23:31.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Mama also wrote one.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.12,1:23:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Do come back again full of vigour.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.76,1:23:37.79,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I have lots of vigour.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.82,1:23:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with all your vigour.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.79,1:23:39.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She got the letter from her mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.86,1:23:42.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And will head home to her father who is waiting.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.23,1:23:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.23,1:23:48.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Saying their goodbyes at the elevator.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.81,1:23:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't cry. {\alphaFF\t(1587,1587,\alpha0)}It really surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.04,1:23:58.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The mother too.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.21,1:24:00.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She tried to keep it in.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.95,1:24:03.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She was able to do it by herself.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.18,1:24:07.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,From now on she will be able to go by herself.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.63,1:24:20.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The bus departed with Kureha on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.94,1:24:31.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As she was bestowed energy{\alphaFF\t(1591,1591,\alpha0)} tears start appearing.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.65,1:24:38.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As she has given away energy{\alphaFF\t(1654,1654,\alpha0)} tears start appearing.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.96,1:24:47.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The mother's handling was so kind.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.61,1:25:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alphaFF\t(0,354,\alpha0)\t(1956,0,\alphaFF}I will do my best.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.28,1:25:07.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since this the mother
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.95,1:25:11.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,recovered so much the nurses were astounded.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.66,1:25:21.73,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Though she was only in there with her mother for 1 hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.73,1:25:23.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.36,1:25:26.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The story from the picture book continued in her dreams.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.30,1:25:28.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Just a bit more and you will pass home.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.20,1:25:30.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Close the picture book.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.61,1:25:34.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's the next bus stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.21,1:25:41.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's still fast asleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.69,1:25:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Young lady. Young lady.{\alphaFF\t(4489,4489,\alpha0)} We arrived. {\alphaFF\t(5657,5657,\alpha0)}We arrived at your home.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.85,1:25:50.99,Studio,,0,0,0,,What a relief.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.76,1:25:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Young lady. {\alphaFF\t(1123,1123,\alpha0)}Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.83,1:25:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.37,1:26:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We arrived to your home.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.17,1:26:02.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Home? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.20,1:26:04.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I was dreaming of my mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.98,1:26:12.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But the errand wasn't just a dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.68,1:26:17.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is the time her father always sleeps so she enters quietly.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.08,1:26:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.35,1:26:22.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was pacing restlessly around the room.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.26,1:26:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You did your best.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.26,1:26:24.99,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I want to give you a letter.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.99,1:26:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it this one?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.93,1:26:26.59,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Um.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.59,1:26:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The letter. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.56,1:26:29.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The letter that her mother handed her.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.96,1:26:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.27,1:26:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alphaFF\t(0,317,\alpha0)\t(2252,0,\alphaFF)}I will now read mama's letter.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.74,1:26:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,To papa,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.37,1:26:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Today {\alphaFF\t(1824,1824,\alpha0)}you believed in Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.38,1:26:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(4255,0,\alphaFF)}Thank you for {\alphaFF\t(1486,1486,\alpha0)\t(4255,0,\alphaFF)}properly sending her off.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.88,1:26:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alphaFF\t(0,590,\alpha0)\t(6129,0,\alphaFF)}Papa, give this award {\alphaFF\t(3727,2737,\alpha0)\t(6129,0,\alphaFF)}for the girl doing her best.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.29,1:27:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alphaFF\t(0,655,\alpha0)}It's tough when you {\alphaFF\t(3124,3124,\alpha0)}have to do what's necessary to fight an illness.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.96,1:27:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's tough but {\alphaFF\t(2093,2093,\alpha0)}I have {\alphaFF\t(5129,5129,\alpha0)}a family. {\alphaFF\t(7565,7565,\alpha0)}I have all of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.54,1:27:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I am happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.58,1:27:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's enjoy the development of a child together {\alphaFF\t(2956,2956,\alpha0)}and embark on a happy life.{\alphaFF\t(6559,6559,\alpha0)}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.35,1:27:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? That's what mom wrote.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.76,1:27:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.82,1:27:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama has...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.69,1:27:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(4595,0,\alphaFF)\t(4595,0,\alphaFF)\t(4562,0,\alphaFF)}This wonderful gold medal. {\alphaFF\t(2159,2159,\alpha0)\t(4595,0,\alphaFF)}She wants to say "here you go, Kureha".
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.80,1:27:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.87,1:27:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hug me.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.31,1:27:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(1852,0,\alphaFF)}You did your best.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.28,1:27:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.91,1:27:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You did your best. You did your best.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.62,1:27:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(2719,0,\alphaFF)}Papa is crying.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.35,1:28:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alphaFF\t(0,393,\alpha0)}And she will keep developing. From here on out.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.99,1:28:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alphaFF\t(0,323,\alpha0)}I'm happy that I get to watch her development.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.36,1:28:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And I want to see much more of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.93,1:28:11.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.03,1:28:14.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And has the father developed through this too?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.34,1:28:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Good girl. {\alphaFF\t(383,383,\alpha0)}Good girl. {\alphaFF\t(684,684,\alpha0)}Good girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.77,1:28:18.81,Studio,,0,0,0,,He hasn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.10,1:28:18.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's no good.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.81,1:28:22.21,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,{\t(3186,0,\alphaFF)}It's hot.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.77,1:28:22.91,Studio,,0,0,0,,It's hot.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.48,1:28:24.38,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,It's hot.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.41,1:28:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.38,1:28:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You did well in going to your mother's.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.28,1:28:27.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,2 weeks later.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.75,1:28:31.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The mother who quickly improved was discharged.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.15,1:28:32.65,Studio,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.72,1:28:32.65,Studio,,0,0,0,,How great.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.05,1:28:34.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Bringing grandad and grandma to go watch the fall colors.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.93,1:28:40.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The sun is shining brightly.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.33,1:28:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alphaFF\t(0,484,\alpha0)\t(4054,0,\alphaFF)\fs45\pos(1166.4,228.2)}Shizuoka ● Morimachi
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.63,1:28:42.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In the best region in Japan for tea, Shizuoka.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.80,1:28:44.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Where two kids are brought up strong.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.83,1:28:54.31,RedFill,,0,0,0,,{\alphaFF\t(0,490,\alpha0)\pos(1244.4,538.6)\t(9065,0,\alphaFF)}Beni\N{\fs40}4 years 1 month
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.87,1:28:54.31,BlueFill,,0,0,0,,{\alphaFF\t(0,490,\alpha0)\t(7025,0,\alphaFF)\pos(204,538.6)}Gen\N{\fs40}3 years 9 months
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.60,1:28:48.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Beni who recently turned 4 and
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.17,1:28:51.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,the 4 months younger Gen who is still 3.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.44,1:28:54.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Even after kindergarten is over they hang out as the familiar duo.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.94,1:28:57.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Even today Gen came to Beni's house to play.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.71,1:29:00.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Beni is pouring tea into the container.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.25,1:29:03.85,WhiteRedBorder,,0,0,0,,We are running out of tea leaves.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.85,1:29:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But we have to bring it tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.42,1:29:09.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,At the kindergarten they must bring tea in every day.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.82,1:29:12.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's to rinse their mouths.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.09,1:29:16.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,At this elementary school tea comes out of the faucet.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.60,1:29:18.60,Studio,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.26,1:29:20.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's not for drinking. Only rinsing.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.30,1:29:22.67,Studio,,0,0,0,,Eh. What is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.37,1:29:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alphaFF\t(0,319,\alpha0)\pos(1221.6,999.4)\t(4190,0,\alphaFF)\fs40}Filmed in 2011.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.94,1:29:27.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It is said that it helps protect against the common cold and influenza.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.54,1:29:30.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As expected from a tea producing region.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.31,1:29:32.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They will go buy tea for gargling.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.95,1:29:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to purchase?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.98,1:29:38.32,WhiteRedBorder,,0,0,0,,Tea for gargling.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.62,1:29:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's exactly it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.69,1:29:42.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He brings Beni's tea container.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.99,1:29:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How kind of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.19,1:29:54.13,RedFill,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1220.4,300.2)\alphaFF\t(0,322,\alpha0)}Home
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.19,1:29:54.13,GreenFill,,0,0,0,,{\alphaFF\t(0,322,\alpha0)\pos(676.8,865)}Tea shop
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.92,1:29:47.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They are going to buy tea for gargling.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.66,1:29:50.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's the same route as on the way to the kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.26,1:29:54.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The mothers have found a safe path with no cars.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.27,1:30:01.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Uwa, looks like it will be a fun little errand.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.14,1:30:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Off you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.31,1:30:04.78,WhiteRedBorder,,0,0,0,,Off we go.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.28,1:30:10.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The two of them depart in a good mood and friendly.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.18,1:30:12.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.85,1:30:15.99,WhiteRedBorder,,0,0,0,,It's kinda scary.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.16,1:30:20.29,WhiteRedBorder,,0,0,0,,For some reason tears are forming.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.29,1:30:22.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She was overcome with loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:24.80,1:30:26.93,WhiteRedBorder,,0,0,0,,{\t(1787,0,\alphaFF)}Want to cry?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.73,1:30:26.93,Studio,,0,0,0,,Want to cry?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.20,1:30:29.34,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\t(1756,0,\alphaFF)}Want to cry?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.97,1:30:32.64,WhiteRedBorder,,0,0,0,,I want to go back to my mother's.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.47,1:30:35.31,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Where mama is, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.31,1:30:37.18,WhiteRedBorder,,0,0,0,,I do want to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.18,1:30:40.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,While saying all that they proceed with smiles.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.75,1:30:42.85,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,It will be fine cause I am with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.35,1:30:46.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Gen is a man. He's reliable.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.82,1:30:50.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Continuing down the straight path.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.03,1:30:57.40,WhiteRedBorder,,0,0,0,,Mr. Sun, {\alphaFF\t(1620,1620,\alpha0)}don't go away, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.40,1:31:00.30,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Mr. Sun,{\alphaFF\t(1586,1586,\alpha0)} don't go away, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.27,1:31:03.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It won't go away just yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.31,1:31:07.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Eh, a quarrel?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.54,1:31:10.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But in fact...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.84,1:31:12.71,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Gen's win.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.71,1:31:14.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They are playing around.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.75,1:31:15.75,Studio,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.88,1:31:17.65,WhiteRedBorder,,0,0,0,,A kappa's leaf.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.88,1:31:21.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What's a kappa's leaf.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.62,1:31:24.99,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Since the kappa is coming
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.99,1:31:27.49,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\t(2124,0,\alphaFF)}this will protect you from getting wet.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.16,1:31:30.70,WhiteRedBorder,,0,0,0,,A kappa will also come for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.70,1:31:34.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A kappa's leaf! To be honest this old guy doesn't have a clue.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.07,1:31:36.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But it's a good overall feeling.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:36.27,1:31:37.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.50,1:31:39.51,WhiteRedBorder,,0,0,0,,Let's eat a rice balls.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.07,1:31:42.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They found a place to eat rice balls.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.51,1:31:43.98,WhiteRedBorder,,0,0,0,,Gen...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:43.98,1:31:46.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Beni has an edamame rice ball.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.48,1:31:47.68,Studio,,0,0,0,,- How nice. \N- Nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.12,1:31:50.05,WhiteRedBorder,,0,0,0,,Delicious.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.05,1:31:52.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And Gen has a seaweed rice ball.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.35,1:31:55.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And there's kelp mixed with the rice.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.46,1:31:59.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They are really relishing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.96,1:32:03.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Even this old guy wants one now.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.50,1:32:07.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Please take care of the litter.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.50,1:32:09.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The always kind Gen.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.54,1:32:12.01,WhiteRedBorder,,0,0,0,,I am going.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.01,1:32:15.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Please wait. I'm getting ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.01,1:32:19.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Their stomachs are full.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.61,1:32:21.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And the sun is pleasantly warm.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.28,1:32:22.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.48,1:32:25.08,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Want to take a break? {\alphaFF\t(1324,1324,\alpha0)}Right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.35,1:32:25.08,WhiteRedBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,1004.2)}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.08,1:32:27.12,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Want to lay down?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.12,1:32:29.06,WhiteRedBorder,,0,0,0,,Lay down?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.16,1:32:31.46,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,It feels good to lay down.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.46,1:32:34.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is a post-feast nap.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.80,1:32:39.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Mr. Sun didn't go away as promised.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.43,1:32:40.50,WhiteRedBorder,,0,0,0,,Here we are.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.50,1:32:42.14,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,We finally arrived.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.14,1:32:45.17,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Mr. Sun, {\alphaFF\t(1317,1317,\alpha0)}don't go away, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.54,1:32:46.41,Studio,,0,0,0,,How nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.44,1:32:50.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Full of playing around 1 hour and 45 minutes have passed since they left.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.31,1:32:52.78,WhiteRedBorder,,0,0,0,,We've arrived so it will be fine from now on.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.31,1:32:55.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Finally time for the errand.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.38,1:32:57.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What type of tea do they need to buy?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.89,1:33:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.19,1:33:02.82,WhiteRedBorder,,0,0,0,,One for the lid, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.82,1:33:04.89,WhiteRedBorder,,0,0,0,,One for the lid, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.13,1:33:11.50,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Tea leaves.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.50,1:33:14.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Gen, nice follow up.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.00,1:33:17.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,First they get to enjoy a tea sample.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.71,1:33:20.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This isn't for gargling.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:20.07,1:33:21.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since this is first-rate tea.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.98,1:33:26.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They appreciate good tea.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.18,1:33:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Will this one be fine?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:28.15,1:33:30.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,No no. No need for first-rate tea.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.38,1:33:32.29,WhiteRedBorder,,0,0,0,,Tea for gargling.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.29,1:33:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You need it for gargling?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.45,1:33:34.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:34.92,1:33:38.73,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's tea for gargling that they need to bring to the kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.73,1:33:41.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,For gargling the cheapest one is sufficient.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.03,1:33:50.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They help pouring it in the containers.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.47,1:33:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How old are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.91,1:33:54.94,WhiteRedBorder,,0,0,0,,4 years old.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:54.07,1:33:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,4 years?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:54.94,1:33:56.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's a bit proud of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.84,1:33:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And you?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.28,1:34:00.81,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,3 years old.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.81,1:34:02.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's a bit frustrating.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.98,1:34:06.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The containers are now full to the brim.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.65,1:34:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.22,1:34:11.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and go home.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.39,1:34:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:12.63,1:34:15.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Mr. Sun waited for them.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.96,1:34:18.36,WhiteRedBorder,,0,0,0,,Today is our first errand.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.36,1:34:21.07,WhiteRedBorder,,0,0,0,,Huge success.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.60,1:34:24.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,No no. The errand isn't over until you get home.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.67,1:34:27.81,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm tired already.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.67,1:34:27.81,WhiteRedBorder,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.81,1:34:29.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Their legs started getting heavy.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.44,1:34:32.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,If they don't hurry home it will start to get dark.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.48,1:34:36.45,WhiteRedBorder,,0,0,0,,Should we take a break here?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.45,1:34:39.85,WhiteRedBorder,,0,0,0,,Want to eat Ramune.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.98,1:34:39.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ramune?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:40.52,1:34:45.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They were told to eat it if they started feeling tired. The mothers prepared it.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.02,1:34:47.96,WhiteRedBorder,,0,0,0,,This is for both of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:52.17,1:34:53.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It revitalized them.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:58.37,1:35:02.68,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\t(3893,0,\alphaFF)}Beni, it's dangerous to go there.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.71,1:35:10.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,If they don't hurry the sun will set.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.76,1:35:23.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Mr. Sun is taking his sweet time for the sake of both of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.07,1:35:27.40,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I can see it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.40,1:35:30.57,WhiteRedBorder,,0,0,0,,The moon is so red.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.57,1:35:32.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's the sun.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.23,1:36:02.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The mothers have turned on all the lights in the house and are waiting.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:08.44,1:36:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Gen.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.64,1:36:13.01,WhiteRedBorder,,0,0,0,,I am home!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:11.21,1:36:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.48,1:36:16.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They returned safely.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:16.38,1:36:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Gen, you have so much strength.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.48,1:36:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Gen is carrying it.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.59,1:36:22.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The kind man, Gen, also reached the goal.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.66,1:36:25.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's been 3 hours and 50 minutes since they left the house.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.39,1:36:27.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They did their best without quarreling.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.56,1:36:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It must've been heavy.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.93,1:36:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You really did your best. \NYou've been a great help.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:31.70,1:36:34.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They got the right tea for gargling.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:36.47,1:36:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Bacteria is being spat out.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.11,1:36:45.04,WhiteRedBorder,,0,0,0,,Let's say cheers with our cups.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.98,1:36:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say cheers with our cups.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:45.04,1:36:47.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's such a nice time when you gargle tea.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.65,1:36:52.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This spring they started junior high school and they both sent us a video.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.65,1:36:56.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They didn't get to do their elementary school graduations.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.85,1:37:01.09,PurpleFill,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1078.8,290.6)\alphaFF\t(0,290,\alpha0\t(7998,0,\alphaFF))}Beni \N{\fs40}Junior High 1 year
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.53,1:37:02.93,WhiteRedBorder,,0,0,0,,It's bitter.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.93,1:37:06.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Even at junior high they still gargle on green tea.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.23,1:37:07.93,BlueFill,,0,0,0,,{\pos(170.4,282.6)\alphaFF\t(0,354,\alpha0)\t(4425,0,\alphaFF)}Gen \N{\fs40}Junior High 1 year
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.40,1:37:09.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They always do it when they wash their hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.07,1:37:13.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It would be nice if life can get back to normal as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.34,1:37:19.81,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Our first errand. {\alphaFF\t(2056,2056,\alpha0)}Huge success!
